//åè½ï¼åææ´ä¸ªURLæ¾åºéé¢æªç¼ç çåæ°ä½¿ç¨myEscapeè¿è¡ç¼ç 
function escapeUrl(s) {
    if (s == null || typeof (s) == "undefined" || s == "") {
        return s;
    }
    if (s && s.href) {  //å¤çæ¿æ¢locationå¯¹è±¡çé®é¢
        s = s.href;
    }
    var pos = s.indexOf("?");
    if (pos < 0) return s;
    var url = s.substring(0, pos + 1);
    var str = s.substring(pos + 1);
    var paramUrl = "";
    if (str.length > 0) {
        var paramAry = str.split("&");
        var paramNameValuePair = [];
        var paramName = "", paramValue = "";
        for (var i = 0, length = paramAry.length; i < length; i++) {
            paramNameValuePair = paramAry[i].split("=");
            if (paramNameValuePair.length === 2) {
                paramName = paramNameValuePair[0];
                try {
                    paramValue = decodeURIComponent(paramNameValuePair[1]);
                } catch (err) {
                    paramValue = paramNameValuePair[1];
                }
                paramValue = encodeURIComponent(paramValue);
                paramUrl += "&" + paramName + "=" + paramValue;
            }
        }
        if (paramAry.length > 0)
            paramUrl = paramUrl.substring(1);
    }
    return url + paramUrl;
}

